  "description": "&lt;div style=\"font-family:&amp;quot;Avenir Next W01&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next W00&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next&amp;quot;, Avenir, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size:16px;\"&gt;&lt;font size=\"4\" style=\"font-family:inherit;\"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Cleveland National Register of Historic Places points&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\"font-family:&amp;quot;Avenir Next W01&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next W00&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next&amp;quot;, Avenir, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size:16px;\"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span style=\"font-family:&amp;quot;Avenir Next W01&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next W00&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next&amp;quot;, Avenir, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size:16px;\"&gt;This is a local copy of National Register of Historic Places point data that is updated by Cleveland City Planning and Landmarks to provide a more up-to-date resource for Cleveland. This is not the authoritative resource directly from the National Park Service.&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div style=\"font-family:&amp;quot;Avenir Next W01&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next W00&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next&amp;quot;, Avenir, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size:16px;\"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\"font-family:&amp;quot;Avenir Next W01&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next W00&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Avenir Next&amp;quot;, Avenir, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size:16px;\"&gt;Cleveland City Planning uses this web layer for our own record-keeping purposes as we track additions and updates to NRHP points. Because the National Park Services GIS assets may take time to be updated or have limited accuracy, we maintain our own copy of NRHP data and present to the public for their use.&lt;/div&gt;",
